Ice watched the battles around her, she stayed in Polar bear mode and
charged back into battle, she used her telepathic powers and picked out
Ares. She flashed back to Lunarpines first battle and realized that Ares was
the one who'd blinded her beloved wolf. Since he was going after her killer
she decided to even the score. She used her tele kinetic powers to kick up a
duststorm to blind the bot, then she charged forward swiping her large paw
at his head.
